a difference if they

00:25:00.270 --> 00:25:01.834
use what you taught them.

00:25:01.834 --> 00:25:03.750
They're only going to
use what you taught them

00:25:03.750 --> 00:25:04.994
if they've learned it.

00:25:04.994 --> 00:25:06.660
And they're much more
likely to learn it

00:25:06.660 --> 00:25:08.140
if they liked or
