00:25:14.906 --> 00:25:15.830
Did they learn it?

00:25:15.830 --> 00:25:16.970
Well, memory
retention is higher,

00:25:16.970 --> 00:25:17.600
and they're quick to read.

00:25:17.600 --> 00:25:18.470
You can learn more, faster.

00:25:18.470 --> 00:25:19.719
You can read the thing faster.

00:25:19.719 --> 00:25:20.725
And did they use it?

00:25:20.725 --> 00:25:22.600
They're more likely to
be shared with others.

00:25:22.600 --> 00:25:25.016
And when lots of people do
something, the culture changes.

